  "body": "  The Negative Powers Rule lets us see how inverse proportionality relationships lead to power models.     Rewrite your formula from , relating the number of times a word appears in English Wikipedia and its rank, with a negative exponent to show that it is a power model.      Rewrite your formula from , relating the wi-fi signal power and distance from a wireless router, with a negative exponent to show that it is a power model.    "
